Finnish Folk Metal version of a decently popular older tune.  Let's hope it's a nice and easy one ^^

Strum pattern, I found out, was basically D-D-DUD for each chord except the intro chords. Intro chords are
single strum. The last verse beginning chord ( Dm ) is a single strum extended chord, but then it goes back to
D-D-DUD pattern.

-Sharky
